com.orchestranetworks.service
Interface SessionPermissions

public interface SessionPermissions

Defines a facade for checking the user's session permissions (access rights or actions) on data spaces, snapshots, data sets, records, and nodes (tables, ...).

See Also:
AccessPermission, ActionPermission
